 Police on Tuesday recovered a portion of the money robbed from the employees of a petrol pump in Barasat on Monday. A gang of five had snatched Rs 3 lakh and fled.

 police team on Tuesday raided a house in Ashoknagar, on the northern fringes of the city, and recovered nearly half the amount. Four people have been detained for interrogation.

